<HEAD><TITLE>INFOTHEQUE SIDA - Infoth&egrave;que SIDA 02/96</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="FFFFFF">
<A HREF="/anais/search"><IMG ALIGN=RIGHT BORDER=0 SRC="/gif/Search2.gif"></A>
<A HREF="INFOTHEQUE.cgi?+9602"><IMG ALIGN=RIGHT BORDER=0 SRC="/gif/Bibliotheque2.gif"></A><IMG ALIGN=left BORDER=0 SRC="INFOTHEQUE/gif/marge.gif"><H2>AIDS INFOTHEK - INFOTHEQUE SIDA</H2><I>Das Magazin der Aids Info Docu Schweiz<BR>Le magazine de Sida Info Doc Suisse</I><BR CLEAR><p><center><b><i>On a constat&eacute; que toute infection "consomme", c'est-&agrave;-dire que l'organisme a besoin de davantage d'&eacute;nergie, de vitamines et de min&eacute;raux. Cela vaut aussi pour l'infection par le VIH.<br>Man hat festgestellt, dass jede Infektion "konsumierend" wirkt, das heisst, der K&ouml;rper braucht mehr Energie, Vitamine und Mineralstoffe. Das gilt auch f&uuml;r die HIV-Infektion.</i></b></center><p><CENTER>
<A HREF="INFOTHEQUE.cgi?9602:12"><IMG BORDER=0 SRC="/gif/left.gif"></A>
<A HREF="INFOTHEQUE.cgi?9602:12.2"><IMG BORDER=0 SRC="/gif/right.gif"></A>
</CENTER>
<UL>
<h3>Whose problem? An HIV/AIDS education package</h3><blockquote><b>Wandsworth Health Promotion Services, Common Body Theatre Company (Ed.)</b><br><i>London, 1990, 24 Min.,  25.-- (mit Begleitmaterial) </i><p>Whose problem? ... is the story of 16 year old David, whose mother is in hospital with AIDS. Unable to cope with the insensitive reactions of those around him, he decides to run away. While packing, he recalls some recent events which have left him feeling isolated and confused. The video is intended for use in schools, colleges, youth centres and other young people venues for groups aged 13+. It is accompanied by a booklet giving ideas for discussion and follow-up activities. <p>David is played by an actor who speaks in English slang. He is at times difficult to understand for foreign ears. The text is, however, printed in extenso in the booklet.</blockquote></UL>
<HR>
<CENTER>
<A HREF="INFOTHEQUE.cgi?9602:12"><IMG BORDER=0 SRC="/gif/left.gif"></A>
<A HREF="INFOTHEQUE.cgi?9602:12.2"><IMG BORDER=0 SRC="/gif/right.gif"></A>
</CENTER>
