<HEAD><TITLE>INFOTHEQUE SIDA - Infoth&egrave;que SIDA 02/96</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="FFFFFF">
<A HREF="/anais/search"><IMG ALIGN=RIGHT BORDER=0 SRC="/gif/Search2.gif"></A>
<A HREF="INFOTHEQUE.cgi?+9602"><IMG ALIGN=RIGHT BORDER=0 SRC="/gif/Bibliotheque2.gif"></A><IMG ALIGN=left BORDER=0 SRC="INFOTHEQUE/gif/marge.gif"><H2>AIDS INFOTHEK - INFOTHEQUE SIDA</H2><I>Das Magazin der Aids Info Docu Schweiz<BR>Le magazine de Sida Info Doc Suisse</I><BR CLEAR><p><center><b><i>On a constat&eacute; que toute infection "consomme", c'est-&agrave;-dire que l'organisme a besoin de davantage d'&eacute;nergie, de vitamines et de min&eacute;raux. Cela vaut aussi pour l'infection par le VIH.<br>Man hat festgestellt, dass jede Infektion "konsumierend" wirkt, das heisst, der K&ouml;rper braucht mehr Energie, Vitamine und Mineralstoffe. Das gilt auch f&uuml;r die HIV-Infektion.</i></b></center><p><CENTER>
<A HREF="INFOTHEQUE.cgi?9602:12.1"><IMG BORDER=0 SRC="/gif/left.gif"></A>
<A HREF="INFOTHEQUE.cgi?9602:12.3"><IMG BORDER=0 SRC="/gif/right.gif"></A>
</CENTER>
<UL>
<h3>Unmasking AIDS</h3><blockquote><b>International Planned Parenthood Federation (Ed.), Illustra Films (Prod.)</b><br><i>London, 1991, 43 Min.,  41.70 (mit Begleitmaterial)</i><p>Unmasking AIDS is about a group of friends who attend a youth club set in a multi-racial area of East London. Ginny's mother Gwen (a family planning worker) helps the young people to produce some improvised dramas on HIV prevention. The real life tensions and dilemmas between Ginny and her mother get mixed up in a 'mask play' which culminates in a dramatic finale. The play shows that men and women of all ages may have worries about HIV infection and that talking honestly about sex can sometimes change negative attitudes and behaviour. The video is accompanied by two teaching guides: "Unmasking AIDS - a different approach to HIV education" and "Activities to explore - using drama in AIDS and family planning work".</blockquote></UL>
<HR>
<CENTER>
<A HREF="INFOTHEQUE.cgi?9602:12.1"><IMG BORDER=0 SRC="/gif/left.gif"></A>
<A HREF="INFOTHEQUE.cgi?9602:12.3"><IMG BORDER=0 SRC="/gif/right.gif"></A>
</CENTER>
