<H3>Vancouver Conference Internet Address</H3>
The World Wide Web address for the XI International
Conference on AIDS (Vancouver, July 7-12, 1996) is:
http://unixg.ubc.ca:780/~aids11/aids96.html (Note that the
last two characters in &quot;aids11&quot; are the digit, while the last
character in &quot;html&quot; is the letter.)
<P>
Due to a misunderstanding, AIDS TREATMENT NEWS #233 published
a different WWW address -- which reaches the Canadian HIV
Trials Network, not the Conference. It is possible to link to
the Conference through the Trials Network site, but the
address above is preferred.
