<H3>Cryptosporidiosis Information Phone/Fax Line</H3>
The U.S. Centers for Disease Control has started a phone and
fax service for information about cryptosporidiosis. Callers
can listen to recorded messages, or receive printed
information by fax. The phone number is 404/330-1242.
