<TD ALIGN=LEFT VALIGN=BOTTOM>
<H2><FONT COLOR="#8000FF">Registration Form<BR>
(HivNet.ch Access Request)</FONT></H2>
</TD>
</TR>

<TR>
<TD></TD>

<TD>Complete the form below to benefit from the free services available
on HivNet.ch. 
<PRE> 

</PRE>
</TD>
</TR>

<TR ALIGN=LEFT VALIGN=CENTER>
<TD VALIGN=TOP><FONT COLOR="#8000FF"><B><FONT SIZE=+1>Choose here:<BR>
</FONT></B><FONT SIZE=-1>(Note: you must complete a new form for each service
you request.)</FONT></FONT></TD>

<TD ALIGN=LEFT VALIGN=TOP><B><FONT COLOR="#8000FF"><FONT SIZE=+1>...to
do this:</FONT></FONT></B><FORM ACTION="/forms/forms.cgi?registrationE" METHOD=POST><BR>
</TD>
</TR>

<TR>
<TD NOWRAP><INPUT TYPE=RADIO NAME="Service" VALUE="Library Requested"><B><I>&quot;Library&quot;</I></B></TD>

<TD>Use the space available on HivNet.ch to share your group's files, publications,
collected data and bibliographies with the rest of the community.</TD>
</TR>

<TR>
<TD><INPUT TYPE=RADIO NAME="Service" VALUE="Forum Requested"><B><I>&quot;Forum&quot;</I></B></TD>

<TD>Open a forum on the Web where your members and the public can discuss
various topics, issues or questions.</TD>
</TR>

<TR>
<TD><INPUT TYPE=RADIO NAME="Service" VALUE="Organizations Requested"><B><I>&quot;Organizations&quot;</I></B></TD>

<TD>List your organization on the HivNet.ch server. Recieve your URL and
begin developing your site on the Web.</TD>
</TR>

<TR ALIGN=LEFT VALIGN=CENTER>
<TD><INPUT TYPE=RADIO NAME="Service" VALUE="Mailing list Requested"><B><I>&quot;Mailing
list&quot;</I></B></TD>

<TD>Create electronic mailing lists to keep your members informed of the
latest developments via E-mail.</TD>
</TR>

<TR>
<TD><INPUT TYPE=RADIO NAME="Service" VALUE="Advice Requested"><B><I>&quot;Advice&quot;</I></B></TD>

<TD>Offer anonymous advice and information. Establish new relations with
your members and the public by helping them find answers to their questions.</TD>
</TR>

<TR>
<TD><INPUT TYPE=RADIO NAME="Service" VALUE="E-mail Requested" CHECKED><B><I>&quot;E-mail&quot;</I></B></TD>

<TD>Establish an E-mail address for your group and subscribe to mailing
lists offered by other organizations on the net.</TD>
</TR>
</TABLE>

