understand the terms or do not agree with them, you should not use this
service.</LI>

<LI>Individual requests for use of these services must be submitted through
an existing AIDS/HIV organization.</LI>

<LI>All infomation given on this form will be held confidential, and only
the <I>Fondation du Pr&eacute;sent</I> and its executive committee have
authorized access. No information about any HivNet.ch participant will
be released without the express permission of the participant.</LI>

