<P><A HREF="http://www.enviroworld.com/index.html">Return to EnviroWorld
home page</A><HR ALIGN=LEFT></P>

<H1 ALIGN=CENTER><IMG SRC="../Images/FlRFPbw.gif" WIDTH="382" HEIGHT="51"
ALIGN="BOTTOM" NATURALSIZEFLAG="3"></H1>

<H1 ALIGN=CENTER><FONT COLOR="#FF0000" SIZE=+4>Don't miss a bid!</FONT></H1>

<P ALIGN=CENTER><TABLE WIDTH="574" BORDER="0" CELLSPACING="2" CELLPADDING=
"0" HEIGHT="804">
<TR>
<TD WIDTH="20%" VALIGN="TOP" HEIGHT="799"><P><B><FONT COLOR="#0099FF">Look What Others<BR>
Are Saying:</FONT></B></P>

<DL>
  <DD><I>&quot;We've won 3 new contracts in just two months on the service.&quot;</I>
  <DD><I></I>&nbsp;
  <DD><I>&quot;The daily service is so timely--sometimes we call for documents
  before they are available-we're way early. So there's plenty of time to
  get ready for the bid&quot;</I>
  <DD><I></I>&nbsp;
  <DD><I>&quot;Not all of the RFPs fit with our company so I pass them along
  to clients who can do that kind of work. Then when they get the contracts,
  they come back to us for sub-contractor work.&quot;</I>
</DL>

<P ALIGN=RIGHT>-Glori Snow,<BR>
American Compliance<BR>
Technologies<BR>
Bartow, Florida</P>

<P ALIGN=CENTER>_____</P>

<P ALIGN=CENTER>A Tampa area Bio-remediation firm reported that in one week,
<B><FONT COLOR="#006600">Fl</FONT><FONT COLOR="#0000FF">o</FONT><FONT COLOR="#006600">rida</FONT><FONT
 COLOR="#FF0000"> RFP </FONT><FONT COLOR="#006600">T</FONT><FONT COLOR="#330099">o</FONT><FONT
 COLOR="#006600">day</FONT></B> reported several RFP leads which all of
their other services combined did not find. They are currently dropping
all of their other services and using <B><FONT COLOR="#006600">Fl</FONT><FONT
 COLOR="#0000FF">o</FONT><FONT COLOR="#006600">rida</FONT><FONT COLOR="#FF0000">
RFP </FONT><FONT COLOR="#006600">T</FONT><FONT COLOR="#330099">o</FONT><FONT
 COLOR="#006600">day</FONT></B> exclusively.</P>

<P ALIGN=CENTER>_____</P>

<P>An East-Central Florida research firm reports that <B><FONT COLOR="#006600">Fl</FONT><FONT
 COLOR="#0000FF">o</FONT><FONT COLOR="#006600">rida</FONT><FONT COLOR="#FF0000">
RFP </FONT><FONT COLOR="#006600">T</FONT><FONT COLOR="#330099">o</FONT><FONT
 COLOR="#006600">day</FONT></B> will save them one staff member who would
otherwise spend a full week going through various sources to look for RFPs.
 With <B><FONT COLOR="#006600">Fl</FONT><FONT COLOR="#0000FF">o</FONT><FONT
 COLOR="#006600">rida</FONT><FONT COLOR="#FF0000"> RFP </FONT><FONT COLOR="#006600">T</FONT><FONT
 COLOR="#330099">o</FONT><FONT COLOR="#006600">day</FONT></B>, they can
use that persons time on more profitable and productive activities.</P>

<P>&nbsp;</P>

<P>&nbsp;</TD>
<TD WIDTH="50%" VALIGN="TOP"><P ALIGN=RIGHT><B><FONT COLOR="#006600" SIZE=+2>What we provide for your
firm:</FONT></B></P>

<UL>
  <LI><P ALIGN=RIGHT><B><FONT COLOR="#006600" SIZE=+1>Fl</FONT><FONT COLOR="#330099"
   SIZE=+1>o</FONT><FONT COLOR="#006600" SIZE=+1>rida</FONT><FONT COLOR="#FF0000"
   SIZE=+1> RFP </FONT><FONT COLOR="#006600" SIZE=+1>T</FONT><FONT COLOR="#330099"
   SIZE=+1>o</FONT><FONT COLOR="#006600" SIZE=+1>day</FONT></B><FONT COLOR="#663300"
   SIZE=+1> provides our customers with bids and proposals presented throughout
  Florida and the surrounding area within 24 hours of their publication in
  the state's newspapers. That gives you plenty of time to prepare for the
  proposal and the pre-bid meeting. Our search is concentrated toward environmentally
  related projects, although we may search additional areas as requested.
  </FONT>
</UL>

<P ALIGN=RIGHT><B><FONT COLOR="#006600" SIZE=+2>Your time is valuable:</FONT></B></P>

<UL>
  <LI><P ALIGN=RIGHT><FONT COLOR="#663300" SIZE=+1>Because our subscribers'
  time is so important we summarize each RFP in an easy to read standard
  format. If additional information is needed we will fax the entire notice
  for free.</FONT>
</UL>

<P ALIGN=RIGHT><B><FONT COLOR="#006600" SIZE=+2>We deliver ASAP!</FONT></B></P>

<UL>
  <LI><P ALIGN=RIGHT><FONT COLOR="#663300" SIZE=+1>We speed delivery via
  e-mail due to the ease with which customers can receive, distribute, and
  store the information, but will distribute via fax if this is your preference.
  </FONT>
</UL>

<P ALIGN=RIGHT><B><FONT COLOR="#006600" SIZE=+2>Try before you buy!</FONT></B></P>

<UL>
  <LI><P ALIGN=RIGHT><B><FONT COLOR="#FF0000" SIZE=+1>To receive a free one
  month trial subscription</FONT></B><FONT COLOR="#663300" SIZE=+1>, </FONT><FONT
   SIZE=+1><A HREF="FRFPTtrialsub.html">complete the trial order form and
  fax it back</A></FONT><FONT COLOR="#663300" SIZE=+1> to </FONT><B><FONT
