<H1 ALIGN=CENTER><IMG SRC="../Images/netbutt.gif" WIDTH="80" HEIGHT="96"
ALIGN="BOTTOM" NATURALSIZEFLAG="3"><BR>
Weekly Summary</H1>

<P ALIGN=CENTER>for</P>

<H1 ALIGN=CENTER>EnviroWorld</H1>

<P ALIGN=CENTER><BR>
<HR></P>

<BLOCKQUOTE>
  <P ALIGN=CENTER><B>Report Period: </B>10-21-96 to 10-27-96</P>
</BLOCKQUOTE>

<H1>DPOs</H1>

<BLOCKQUOTE>
  <P>Distinct Points of Origin = A unique address from which a browser connects
  to a Web site on the Internet</P>
  <BLOCKQUOTE>
    <UL>
      <LI>Total DPOsThis Week *: <B>989</B>
      <LI>Total Last Week : <B>1104</B>
      <LI>Daily Average This Week<B>: 176</B>
    </UL>
    <P><BR>
    <BR>
    <B>DPO Breakdown of Access by Category</B></P>
    <UL>
      <LI>International 6.9%
      <LI>Unknown 27.4%
      <LI>Commercial 23.5%
      <LI>Educational 19.4%
      <LI>Government 1.8%
      <LI>Military 0.9%
      <LI>Network 19.1%
      <LI>Organization 1.3%
    </UL>
  </BLOCKQUOTE>
</BLOCKQUOTE>

<H1><HR ALIGN=LEFT>PITs</H1>

<BLOCKQUOTE>
  <P>Page Information Transfer = The successful transfer of the text of a
  web page to a browser</P>
  <BLOCKQUOTE>
    <P><B>Total PITs/</B>% Abandonment</P>
    <UL>
      <LI>Total This Week: <B>4921</B>/0.30%
      <LI>Total Last Week: <B>4797</B>/1.58%
      <LI>Daily Average This Week: <B>703</B>/0.30%
    </UL>
    <P><BR>
    Total Page Information Transfers (PITs) by Day</P>
    <UL>
      <LI><B>Monday </B>804
      <LI><B>Tuesday </B>820
      <LI><B>Wednesday </B>911
      <LI><B>Thursday </B>850
      <LI><B>Friday </B>727
      <LI><B>Saturday </B>451
      <LI><B>Sunday </B>358
    </UL>
  </BLOCKQUOTE>
</BLOCKQUOTE>

<P><HR ALIGN=LEFT></P>

<BLOCKQUOTE>
  <BLOCKQUOTE>
    <P><BR>
    <B><I>DPO</I></B><I> - Distinct Point of Origin<BR>
    A unique address from which a browser connects to a Web site on the Internet<BR>
    <BR>
    <B>PIT</B> - Page Information Transfer<BR>
    The successful transfer of the text of a web page to a browser<BR>
    <BR>
    <B>Abandonment</B><BR>
    The percent of requested pages which are not successfully transferred.</I></P>
  </BLOCKQUOTE>
</BLOCKQUOTE>

<P><B><I><BR>
<BR>
</I></B>* Does not double count multiple visits by any single DPO. <BR>
