<H1 ALIGN=CENTER><IMG SRC="../Images/EWlogobig.gif" WIDTH="353" HEIGHT=
"104" ALIGN="BOTTOM" NATURALSIZEFLAG="3"></H1>

<H1 ALIGN=CENTER><A HREF="#anchor345766">Welcome to EnviroWorld!</A><A 
NAME="anchor345766"></A></H1>

<BLOCKQUOTE>
  <P><B>EnviroWorld</B> is the online Daily Environmental Industry News service
  of <B>Florida Environments</B> magazine. Our magazine is ten years old
  and has 40,000 monthly readers within Florida's environmental industry
  and conservation communities. We are based in Gainesville, Florida (the
  United States' #1 most livable city, according to <B>Money</B> magazine)
  and have a news bureau in Tallahassee.</P>
  <P>EnviroWorld has advertising opportunities for organizations interested
  in penetrating the nation's third largest environmental market. Click here
  to send us e-mail and <A HREF="mailto:sales@enviroworld.com">we'll contact
  you with ad rates</A>, etc.</P>
  <P><BR>
  <B>EnviroWorld</B> is aimed at increasing our coverage of Florida's important
  environmental news as a service to our readers AND <A HREF="support.html">offering
  interested parties from around the world access to Florida's considerable
  environmental expertise</A>. This state has the most delicate environment
  in the USA, among the nation's leading environmental protection regulatory
  systems, and a collection of the most experienced and brightest environmental
  professionals, academics, and activists in the world. There is much to
  be learned from Florida's experiences and the state has many needs of the
  world's experts too. Hopefully, <B>EnviroWorld</B> can help link information
  needs with resources. <A HREF="mailto:info@enviroworld.com">Let us know
  how we're doing.</A></P>
</BLOCKQUOTE>

