<HTML>
<HEAD>
    <TITLE></TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY LINK="#00ff00" BGCOLOR="#ccf5cc">
<P><CENTER><IMG SRC="../Images/feaa.gif" WIDTH="258" HEIGHT="101" ALIGN=
"BOTTOM" NATURALSIZEFLAG="3" BORDER="1"></CENTER>
<H3><CENTER>Florida Environmental Assessors <BR>
Association, Inc. (FEAA)<HR></CENTER>
</H3>
<H1><CENTER>Mission</CENTER>
</H1>
<P><CENTER>The Florida Environmental Assessors Association, Inc. (FEAA),
is a not-for-profit organization dedicated to the advancement of professionalism
in the field of contamination related environmental consultation.<BR>
<BR>
FEAA continues to develop programs in education, professional standards
of practice and certification to enhance the professional assessor, the
environmental industry and public safety.</CENTER>
<P><B>FEAA Objectives include:<BR>
</B>
<UL>
  <LI>The establishment of industry standards and public confidence in the
performance of environmental site assessment services. 
  <LI>The maintenance of Florida specific Guidance Standards of Practice
for Phase I ESAs and the development of Standards of Practice for Confirmatory
Studies. 
  <LI>The capability to assure that Certified Environmental Assessors provide
services in accordance with ethical guidelines and approved Standards of
Practice. 
  <LI>Coordination with other organizations related to environmental consultation
and services and liaison with industry development efforts. 
  <LI>The evolution of environmental site assessment standards, education,
and certification with market demands, laws, and appropriate regulations.
</UL>
<BR>
<B>FEAA offers to its members:</B>
<UL>
  <LI>Ongoing development of standards for due diligence and appropriate
inquiry in performance of ESA's. 
  <LI>Training in assessment methodology, education in environmental science
and creation of professional practice guidelines. 
  <LI>Opportunities to practice in FEAA certification and education programs
as well as committees. 
</UL>
<HR><BR>
<P><CENTER><A HREF="FEAA.html">Home</A> | <A HREF="FEAAmiss.html">Mission</A><BR>
<A HREF="FEAAcert.html">Certification</A> | <A HREF="FEAApro.html">Professionalism</A><BR>
<A HREF="FEAAmem.html">Membership</A> | <A HREF="FEAAinfo.html">For Additional
Information</A></CENTER>
<P><I></I>
</BODY>
</HTML>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO>WT18-B28-348</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA033-000674-B048-265</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.enviroworld.com:80/Resources/FEAAcert.html 205.229.48.145 19970209174516 text/html 5417
