<TD><H1 ALIGN=CENTER>How to Respond to a Listing(s) in the SWIX Clearinghouse
Catalog</H1>

<P>If you locate a material available or wanted listing(s) that is of interest
to you, follow the directions below for completing the Response Form.</P>

<P ALIGN=CENTER><B>Directions for Responding to a Listing(s)</B></P>

<P ALIGN=CENTER><TABLE WIDTH="350" BORDER="0" CELLSPACING="2" CELLPADDING=
"0">
<TR>
<TD VALIGN="TOP">1.</TD>
<TD>Fill in the Material and Code Number of the listing(s) you have an interest
in on the Response Form.</TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD VALIGN="TOP">2.</TD>
<TD><P>Fax or Mail the Response Form to:</P>

<P><B><I>Southern Waste Information Exchange Clearinghouse</I></B><I> <BR>
Fax: (904) 385-4020 <BR>
Post Office Box 960 <BR>
Tallahassee, FL 32302</I></P>

<P><B>OR</B></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD VALIGN="TOP">3.</TD>
<TD>You can send an E-mail <A HREF="mailto:swix@mailer.fsu.edu"><I>swix@mailer.fsu.edu</I>
</A>to SWIX with the listings you are interested in.</TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD VALIGN="TOP">4.</TD>
<TD>Phone (800) 441-SWIX if you have questions or need assistance in responding.</TD></TR>
</TABLE>
<HR></P>

