<P ALIGN=CENTER><HR></P>

<P><A NAME="anchor218005"></A><B>Exposure </B>is very cost-effective visibility
for organizations seeking to improve their returns in the second largest
environmental market in the United States! We have opportunities to fit
any size organization. Help us and we can help you. If you want to have
<B>EnviroWorld</B> contact you, <A HREF="mailto:info@enviroworld.com">e-mail
in your request here</A>. Or call 352-373-1401 for more information. <BR>
</P>

